          <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">relatives</ENAMEX> (Figure <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">3</NUMEX>). The multiple alignment shows that
          the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Bro-N</ENAMEX> domains contain <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> highly conserved aromatic
          or hydrophobic <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">residues</ENAMEX> at <TIMEX TYPE="TIME">the end of the second</TIMEX> and
          <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">fourth</NUMEX> conserved strands, a pattern that is reminiscent
