        were conducted using the PSI-BLAST program with either a
        single sequence or an alignment used as the query, with a
        profile-inclusion expectation (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">E</ENAMEX>) value threshold of <NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">0.01</NUMEX>,
        and were iterated until <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">convergence</TIMEX> [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">35, 36</TIMEX>]. If
        whole-length <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">proteins</ENAMEX> were used, the searches were carried
